
Trim a file:
ffmpeg -i Harry\ Potter\ and\ the\ Half-Blood\ Prince.m4v -ss 1 -codec: copy -map 0:v -map 0:a Harry\ Potter\ and\ the\ Half-Blood\ Prince\ 3.m4v


Change a movie title:
ffmpeg -i Harry\ Potter\ and\ the\ Chamber\ of\ Secrets.m4v -metadata title="Harry Potter and the Chamber of Secrets" -codec: copy -map 0:v -map 0:a Harry\ Potter\ and\ the\ Chamber\ of\ Secrets\ 2.m4v
